Package semsim.reading

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractRDFreader
    Class for working with SemSim annotations that are serialized in RDF format
    CASAreader
    Class for working with annotations stored in Combine Archive semantic annotation (CASA) files.
    CellMLreader
    Class for reading in a CellML model into a SemSimModel object.
    JSimProjectFileReader
    Class for creating SemSim model representations of the models in a JSim Project (.proj) file.
    MIRIAMannotation
    Class for working with annotations formatted according to MIRIAM guidelines
    MMLtoXMMLconverter
    Class for converting JSim's MML code into JSim's XMML format
    ModelClassifier
    Class for determining the format in which models and associated files are stored
    ModelReader
    Base class for readers of all file types
    OMEXmanifestReader
    Contains methods for reading an OMEX archive
    ReferenceTermNamer
    Class for looking up human-readable names for reference URIs
    SBMLreader
    Class for converting an SBML document into the SemSim format
    SemSimComponentImporter
    This class provides methods for importing submodels and units from other models.
    SemSimOWLreader
    Class for reading a SemSim .owl file and creating a SemSimModel object containing the modeling information contained therein.
    SemSimRDFreader
    Class for reading RDF-formatted SemSim annotations as stored within XML-formatted modeling documents (CellML, SBML, or JSim project files).
    XMMLreader
    Class for reading in information about a model that is serialized in JSim's XMML format (an XML-based format for representing an MML model)
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ModelClassifier.ModelType
    Enum of the different file types supported by SemSim
